7Z07SXKY01.html|accessdate=14 September 2013|newspaper=Yomiuri News Paper|date=11 March 2011 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140216104627/http://www.bloomberg.co.jp/news/123-LI467Z07SXKY01.html |archivedate= 16 February 2014 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"After Fukushima: A Survey of Corruption in the Global Nuclear Power Industry\">{{cite book |url=  |title=After Fukushima: A Survey of Corruption in the Global Nuclear Power Industry |author=Richard Tanter |date=October\u2013December 2013|volume= 37 |issue=4 |work=Asian Perspective}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"AlJaz20120705\">{{cite web |title=Japan says Fukushima disaster was 'man-made'|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/asia-pacific/2012/07/2012755496885199.html|work=Al Jazeera and agencies|publisher=AL Jazeera English|accessdate=9 July 2012|date=5 July 2012 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140130075242/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/asia-pacific/2012/07/2012755496885199.html |archivedate= 30 January 2014 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"AlJaz20120723\">{{cite web |title=Japan nuclear plants 'still not safe' |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/asia-pacific/2012/07/20127236623434937.html |publisher=Al Jazeera Online|accessdate=29 July 2012 |date=23 July 2012 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140416085813/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/asia-pacific/2012/07/20127236623434937.html |archivedate= 16 April 2014 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"aljazeera\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/asia-pacific/2011/08/2011810142915166342.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110831170137/http://english.aljazeera.net/news/asia-pacific/2011/08/2011810142915166342.html|url-status = dead|title=Citizen group tracks down Japan's radiation|first=Dahr|last=Jamail|archivedate=31 August 2011|website=www.aljazeera.com}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Amory Lovins 2011\">{{cite web |url=http://www.rmi.org/Knowledge-Center/Library/2011-09_GaikoSoftEnergyPaths |title=Soft Energy Paths for the 21st Century |author=Amory Lovins |year=2011 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224094312/http://www.rmi.org/Knowledge-Center/Library/2011-09_GaikoSoftEnergyPaths |archivedate=24 December 2013 |url-status=dead  }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Areas to which evacuation orders have been issued\">{{cite web |url=http://www.meti.go.jp/english/earthquake/nuclear/roadmap/pdf/20130807_01.pdf|title=Areas to which evacuation orders have been issued|date=7 August 2013}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"asahi\">[http://www.asahi.com/english/TKY201104060126.html Fukushima No. 1 plant designed on 'trial-and-error' basis], ''Asahi Shimbun'', 7 April 2011. {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110407215925/http://www.asahi.com/english/TKY201104060126.html |date=7 April 2011}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"asahi16\">{{cite news |url=http://ajw.asahi.com/article/behind_news/politics/AJ201310250045 |title=Abe dismisses Koizumi's call for zero nuclear power plants |work=[[Asahi Shimbun]] |date=25 October 2013 |accessdate=30 December 2013 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413220411/http://ajw.asahi.com/article/behind_news/politics/AJ201310250045 |archivedate=13 April 2014 |url-status=dead  }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Asahi20120723\">{{cite news |title=Update: Government panel blasts lack of 'safety culture' in nuclear accident |url=http://ajw.asahi.com/article/0311disaster/fukushima/AJ201207230081 |accessdate=29 July 2012 |newspaper=The [[Asahi Shimbun]] |date=23 July 2012 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413220232/http://ajw.asahi.com/article/0311disaster/fukushima/AJ201207230081 |archivedate=13 April 2014 |url-status=dead  }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"bas111\">{{cite journal |url=http://bos.sagepub.com/content/early/2012/02/29/0096340212440359.full.pdf+html |title=Fukushima in review: A complex disaster, a disastrous response |author1=Yoichi Funabashi |author2=Kay Kitazawa |date=1 March 2012 |journal=Bulletin of the Atomic Scientists|volume=68 |issue=2 |pages=9 |bibcode=2012Bu