om/2011/12/breaking-news-fukushima-increasing-leakage-iodine-131/ |date=24 December 2013}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Fukushima-Related Measurements by the CTBTO\">{{cite web |url=http://www.ctbto.org/press-centre/highlights/2011/fukushima-related-measurements-by-the-ctbto/fukushima-related-measurements-by-the-ctbto-page-1/ |title=Fukushima-Related Measurements by the CTBTO |work=CTBTO Press Release 13 April 2011 |accessdate=17 May 2012 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110505005906/http://www.ctbto.org/press-centre/highlights/2011/fukushima-related-measurements-by-the-ctbto/fukushima-related-measurements-by-the-ctbto-page-1/ |archivedate=5 May 2011 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Fukushima: Background on Fuel Ponds\">{{cite web |url=http://www.world-nuclear.org/info/Safety-and-Security/Safety-of-Plants/Appendices/Fukushima--Fuel-Ponds-Background/ |title=Fukushima: Background on Fuel Ponds |format=PDF |accessdate=23 November 2013 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016010133/http://www.world-nuclear.org/info/Safety-and-Security/Safety-of-Plants/Appendices/Fukushima--Fuel-Ponds-Background/ |archivedate=16 October 2013 |url-status=dead  }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Fukushima: Fallout of fear\">{{cite journal |last=Brumfiel|first=Geoff|title=Fukushima: Fallout of fear|journal=Nature|volume=493|issue=7432|pages=290\u201393|doi=10.1038/493290a|pmid=23325191|date=Jan 2013|bibcode=2013Natur.493..290B}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"guardian\">''[[The Guardian]]'' (22 August 2011)[https://www.theguardian.com/world/2011/aug/22/japan-nuclear-disaster-radiation-levels residents may never return to radiation-hit homes] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110823190201/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/aug/22/japan-nuclear-disaster-radiation-levels |date=23 August 2011}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"guardian-20140310\">{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/environment/2014/mar/10/fukushima-operator-dump-contaminated-water-pacific |title=Fukushima operator may 