{"title_page": "Arjun (Firoz Khan)", "text_new": "{{BLP sources|date=September 2013}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2019}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=February 2016}}\n\n'''Arjun''' is an [[India]]n actor, best known for playing the hero character of [[Arjuna]] in [[B. R. Chopra]]'s television serialisation of the ancient Indian history ''[[Mahabharat (1988 TV series)|Mahabharat]]''.<ref>{{cite news |url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-01-20/tv/30646770_1_marathi-films-film-industry-small-screen |title=A film on Mahabharata |publisher=The Times Of India |date=20 January 2012 |accessdate=2012-04-18}}</ref> He has also acted in a number of [[Hindi language]] movies.\n\nHe is an alumnus of Smt. MMK College of Commerce and Economics.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mmkcollege.org/alumni-esteemed.asp |title=Alumni |publisher=Smt. MMK College of Commerce & Economics |accessdate=2012-04-18}}</ref>\n\n== Filmography ==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Other notes\n|-\n| 1984\n| ''[[Manzil Manzil]]''\n| Rupesh\n|\n|-\n| 1985\n| ''[[Zabardast]]''\n| Bikram Singh\n|\n|-\n| 1986\n| ''[[Swati (1986 film)|Swati]]''\n| Manohar Joshi\n|\n|-\n| 1986\n| ''[[Mazloom]]''\n| Rajan Vijay Singh\n|\n|-\n| 1987\n| ''[[Swayam Krushi]]''\n| Chinna\n| Telugu Movie\n|-\n| 1988\n| ''[[Kanwarlal]]''\n| Jaggan Singh\n| \n|-\n| 1988\n| ''[[Qayamat Se Qayamat Tak]]''\n| Ratan Singh\n| \n|-\n| 1988\n| ''[[Khatron Ke Khiladi (1988 film)|Khatron Ke Khiladi]]''\n| Arjun Singh\n| \n|-\n| 1988\n| ''[[Jungle Ki Beti]]''\n| \n| \n|-\n| 1988 - 1990\n| ''[[Mahabharat (1988 TV series)|Mahabharat]]''\n| Arjun\n| TV series \n|-\n| 1989\n| ''Ajeeb Itefaq''\n| Singer\n| Guest Role\n|-\n| 1990\n| ''[[Sher Dil]]''\n| Rapist\n| \n|-\n| 1991\n| ''[[Naya Zaher]]'' \n| Inspector Vikram\n| \n|-\n| 1992\n| ''[[Kal Ki Awaz]]''\n| DSP Singh\n| \n|-\n| 1992\n| ''[[Jigar]]''\n| Duryodhan\n| \n|-\n| 1992\n| ''[[Tirangaa]]''\n| Rasik Nath Gundaswamy\n| \n|-\n| 1